========================================

INTERVIEW QUESTION
========================================

Q. Why do we cast WebDriver to
TakesScreenshot?

A.
getScreenshotAs() method belongs to
TakesScreenshot Interface.
WebDriver reference does not directly
expose this method, so casting is required.

----------------------------------------

Q. Is TakesScreenshot required for
Element Screenshot?

A.
No.

WebElement directly provides
getScreenshotAs() method.

Therefore no casting is required.

